name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: file.bytes-per-checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  file.stream-buffer-size

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.client.job.retry-interval
description:
The delay between getJob retries in ms for retries configured
  with yarn.app.mapreduce.client.job.max-retries.

name: ha.health-monitor.check-interval.ms
description: How often to check the service.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.pathcache.expire-after-access-minutes
description:
The length of time after an entry is last accessed that it
    should be automatically removed.

name: mapreduce.task.userlog.limit.kb
description: The maximum size of user-logs of each task in KB. 0 disables the cap.

name: ha.failover-controller.cli-check.rpc-timeout.ms
description: Timeout that the CLI (manual) FC waits for monitorHealth, getServiceState
